Function Reference/is dynamic sidebar « WordPress Codex
-----------

This [Conditional Tag](/Conditional_Tags "Conditional Tags") checks if
the current [sidebar](/Sidebars "Sidebars") has active widgets. This is
a boolean function, meaning it returns either TRUE or FALSE.

Usage
-----

`  <?php is_dynamic_sidebar(); ?> `

Parameters
----------

This tag does not accept any parameters.

Return Values
-------------

 `(boolean)` 
:   True if the current sidebar has active widgets, otherwise the
    function returns false

Examples
--------

Change Log
----------

Since: 2.2.0

Source File
-----------

`is_dynamic_sidebar()` is located in `wp-includes/widgets.php`.

